lead_paragraph: Venus Williams, troubled by the injured wrist that had kept her idle since Wimbledon, was beaten, 6-3 6-0, yesterday by the 17-year-old qualifier Agnieszka Radwanska of Poland in the second round of the Luxembourg Championship.
